Package neureka.backend.api

Class ExecutionCall<DeviceType extends Device>

java.lang.Object
neureka.backend.api.ExecutionCall<DeviceType>
Type Parameters:
DeviceType - The Device implementation targeted by an instance of this ExecutionCall!
public class ExecutionCall<DeviceType extends Device>
extends java.lang.Object
This class is a simple container holding relevant arguments needed to execute on a targeted Device which is specified by the type parameter below. It also holds a context map responsible for storing operation specific variables.
